headline: Trump order on scalping 'partially helpful' for Live Nation, but questions remain
summary: Investing.com -- On Monday evening at the White House, U.S. President Donald Trump, joined by music icon Kid Rock, signed an executive order cracking down on price gouging and ticket scalping in the entertainment market.
